ax`和`rrt`显著变高，尤其是`rrt_max`在`adservice-2`的变动非常大。\n   - **Evidence**: `rrt_max` 由正常时的 42336.0 上升到 43894.4。另有 `client_error_ratio` 上升，说明服务请求失败或响应超时。\n   - **Component**: `adservice-2`\n\n2. **redis-cart-0 (Pod Level)**\n   - **Reason**: `pod_cpu_usage`增高，尽管不如AdService显著，但结合可能导致的Redis性能瓶颈需要关注。\n   - **Evidence**: `pod_cpu_usage` 从正常的最高99th percentile (P99) 变动到0.02。\n   - **Component**: `redis-cart-0`\n\n3. **cartservice-1**\n   - **Reason**: `client_error_ratio` 大幅上升。\n   - **Evidence**: 错误请求比例提示有系统级响应问题。\n   - **Component**: `cartservice-1`\n\n4. **Node: aiops-k8s-06**\n   - **Reason**: `node_memory_usage_rate`变化显著。\n   - **Evidence**: 读取正常 median 值到故障时 median 变化为 29.44 下降到 21.4。\n   - **Component**: `Node aiops-k8s-06`\n\n5. **Node: aiops-k8s-08**\n   - **Reason**: 重要Pod (`redis-cart-0`, `adservice-2`) 处于该节点上，需注意Node对这些服务的影响。\n   - **Evidence**: 多个受影响的Pod都位于该Node上。\n   - **Component**: `Node aiops-k8s-08`\n\n### Output Result\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"client_error_ratio\", \"error_ratio\", \"rrt_max\", \"pod_cpu_usage\", \"node_memory_usage_rate\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice-2\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant increase in rrt_max causing service disruptions.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max increased from a normal median of 42336.0 to a fault median of 43894.4.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"redis-cart-0\",\n      \"reason\": \"Increased pod_cpu_usage potentially causing Redis performance issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"pod_cpu_usage changed from normal distribution.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice-1\",\n      \"reason\": \"High client error ratio indicating response issues.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Client error ratio increased significantly.\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"Node aiops-k8s-06\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant change in node_memory_usage_rate observed.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"The median usage rate dropped from 29.44 to 21.4